<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shēn shàng níng jù zhe mín zú hún 迦南676</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shēn shàng níng jù zhe níng jù zhe mín zú hún, shí kè bù huì wàng jì wǒ men shì zhōng guó rén.
 xīn shí shí lián zhe, dà shān de shēn chù. nà lǐ yǒu wǒ men zuì qīn de rén.
 yào fān guò qī qiān qī bǎi qī shí qī zuò shān, yào tàng guò qī qiān qī bǎi qī shí qī tiáo hé.
 zhí dào yǒu rén de de fāng dōu zǒu biàn, wǒ men cái gān xīn.
 yīn wèi shén de ài shì gěi shì shàng de měi yī gè rén.
 bù guǎn shì nǐ wǒ chóu dí, shì nǐ de qīn rén, dōu shì bǎo guì de líng hún.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>676</hymn_number>
</song>